#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:58
msgid ""
"* To remove the SiteGround section from your WordPress admin you need to "
"deactivate the SiteGround Central plugin."
msgstr ""
"* Para eliminar la sección de SiteGround de tu administrador de WordPress, "
"necesitas desactivar el plugin SiteGround Central."

