#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:16
msgid ""
"Bulletproof your website security in a few clicks against a range of "
"security breaches, including brute-force attacks, malware threats and bots."
msgstr ""
"Asegura a prueba de balas la seguridad de tu sitio web en unos pocos clics "
"contra una variedad de vulneraciones de seguridad, incluyendo ataques de "
"fuerza bruta, amenazas de malware y bots."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:20
msgid "Caching"
msgstr "Caché"

