msgstr "Conexión exitosa."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:11
msgid "Domain"
msgstr "Dominio"

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:73
msgid "Email Marketing"
msgstr "Marketing por correo electrónico"

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:57
msgid "Email Marketing Banner"
msgstr "Banner de Email Marketing"

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:67
msgid ""
"Email marketing is active. Start adding custom forms now to grow your "
"audience."
msgstr ""
"El marketing por correo electrónico está activo. Comience a agregar "
"formularios personalizados ahora para hacer crecer su audiencia."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:64
msgid ""
"Enable the connection to Email Marketing by pasting your secret connection "
"token."
msgstr ""
"Habilita la conexión a Email Marketing pegando tu token de conexión secreto."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:4
#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:61
msgid "Error"
msgstr "Error"

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:13
msgid ""
"Essential defenses are already active. Want even more protection? Add extra "
"security layers here."
msgstr ""
"Las defensas esenciales ya están activas. ¿Quieres aún más protección? Añade "
"capas de seguridad adicionales aquí."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:74
msgid "Expires"
msgstr "Caduca"

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:42
msgid "External. Give it a better home."
msgstr "Externo. Dale un mejor hogar."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:70
msgid ""
"Find your secret connection token under Email Marketing dashboard > Connect "
"Websites, then paste it here to connect."
msgstr ""
"Encuentra tu token de conexión secreta en el panel de Email Marketing > "
"Conectar sitios web, luego pégalos aquí para conectar."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:28
msgid ""
"Get Essential features for <strong>free</strong> with your plan. Our "
"powerful CDN caches your content across the world. This results in quicker "
"load times and happier visitors."
msgstr ""
"Obtén características esenciales <strong>gratis</strong> con tu plan. "
"Nuestro potente CDN almacena en caché tu contenido en todo el mundo. Esto "
"resulta en tiempos de carga más rápidos y visitantes más felices."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:35
msgid ""
"Get Essential features for <strong>free</strong> with your plan. Our Site "
"Scanner monitors your website for malware and vulnerabilities."
msgstr ""
"Obtén funciones esenciales <strong>gratis</strong> con tu plan. Nuestro "
"Escáner de Sitios monitorea tu sitio web en busca de malware y "
"vulnerabilidades."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:54
msgid "Grow With Easy Email Marketing"
msgstr "Crecé con Easy Email Marketing"

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:59
msgid "Hello, "
msgstr "Hola, "

