#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:18
msgid "Speed Optimizer by SiteGround"
msgstr "Optimizador de velocidad por SiteGround"

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:55
msgid ""
"Stop letting your visitors walk away. Every person who visits your site is a "
"potential customer—don't lose them. Activate the SiteGround Email Marketing "
"plugin to start capturing leads instantly."
msgstr ""
"Deja de permitir que tus visitantes se vayan. Cada persona que visita tu "
"sitio es un cliente potencial, no los pierdas. Activa el plugin de Email "
"Marketing de SiteGround para empezar a capturar leads al instante."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:5
msgid "Success"
msgstr "Éxito"

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:41
msgid "Swap for a custom domain."
msgstr "Cambia por un dominio personalizado."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:40
msgid "System. Make it official."
msgstr "Sistema. Hazlo oficial."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:52
msgid ""
"The SiteGround AI Agent simplifies website management by acting as a 24/7 "
"expert assistant that uses natural language to create content, update "
"plugins, manage WooCommerce products, and more."
msgstr ""
"El Agente de IA de SiteGround simplifica la gestión de sitios web actuando "
"como un asistente experto disponible las 24 horas que utiliza lenguaje "
"natural para crear contenido, actualizar plugins, gestionar productos de "
"WooCommerce y más."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:22
msgid ""
"The Speed Optimizer plugin is a free WordPress performance-boosting solution "
"to improve user experience, increase conversion rates and drive more traffic."
msgstr ""
"El plugin Speed Optimizer es una solución gratuita de WordPress para mejorar "
"el rendimiento, mejorar la experiencia del usuario, aumentar las tasas de "
"conversión y atraer más tráfico."

#. Description of the plugin
msgid ""
"This plugin is designed to provide you with an easy start of your next "
"WordPress project!"
msgstr ""
"¡Este plugin está diseñado para proporcionarte un comienzo fácil de tu "
"próximo proyecto WordPress!"

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:66
msgid "Token can not be empty."
msgstr "El token no puede estar vacío."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:45
msgid "tokens"
msgstr "tokens"

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:43
msgid "Transfer your domain today."
msgstr "Transfiere tu dominio hoy."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:84
msgid "used"
msgstr "utilizado"

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:75
msgid "View details in"
msgstr "Ver detalles en"

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:77
msgid "WordPress Assistance"
msgstr "Asistencia de WordPress"

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:19
msgid ""
"You're off to a fast start with core caching. Boost your speed even further "
"by activating more features."
msgstr ""
"Con el almacenamiento en caché básico, ya tienes un buen comienzo. Aumenta "
"aún más la velocidad activando más funciones."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:25
msgid "Your site is now cached through our CDN servers."
msgstr ""
"Tu sitio ahora está en caché a través de nuestros servidores CDN. Actualiza "
"a Premium desde tu Área de Cliente para habilitar funciones avanzadas, "
"incluyendo el “modo Bajo Ataque”."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:30
msgid ""
"Your site is now cached through our CDN servers. Upgrade to Premium from "
"your Client Area to enable advanced features, including \\\"Under Attack "
"mode\\\"."
msgstr ""
"Tu sitio ahora está en caché a través de nuestros servidores CDN. Actualiza "
"a Premium desde tu Área de Cliente para habilitar funciones avanzadas, "
"incluyendo el “modo Bajo Ataque”."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:32
msgid "Your site is now monitored by our Site Scanner service."
msgstr "Su sitio ahora es monitoreado por nuestro servicio Site Scanner."

#: /chroot/plugins/wordpress-starter/vendor/siteground/siteground-dashboard-notifications/assets/react-strings.php:37
msgid ""
"Your site is now monitored by our Site Scanner service. Upgrade to Premium "
"to enable additional features, including advanced scans, quarantine, and "
"cleanup."
msgstr ""
"Su sitio ahora está monitorizado por nuestro servicio de Site Scanner. "
"Actualice a Premium para habilitar características adicionales, incluyendo "
"análisis avanzados, cuarentena y limpieza."
